<h1>Movies Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>
This Privacy Policy describes the type of information that Movies, LLC ("Movies", "we", or "us") collects from and about you when you access or use the Movies website, www.moviesanywhere.com, download or use the Movies mobile or other application, or use or access any of our other services, features, tools, or materials offered from time to time by Movies and where the Movies Privacy Policy is posted (the "Services"). It also explains how we handle and may share or disclose information collected through the Services, as well as your ability to control certain uses of it.</p>
